{
  "chapter": 30,
  "chapter_summary": "本章讲述辛捷重伤昏迷，凌风用灵玉神泉为其疗伤。辛捷醒来后诉说方少魌投海自尽之事，二人决定先往山东探望苏蕙芷。途中听闻天竺高手挑战中原武林，遂赶往奎山。奎山大会上，天竺高手加大尔与峨嵋苦庵上人激战百余招，苦庵不敌认输。危急关头，武林之秀孙倚重及时出现，一掌震退加大尔，暂解危局。",
  "dialogues": [
    {
      "speaker": "char_ling_feng",
      "speaker_name": "凌风",
      "listener": "char_xin_jie",
      "text": "捷弟，你可好了一点吗？",
      "tone": "担心",
      "chapter": 30,
      "line_start": 12,
      "line_end": 12
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ling_feng",
      "speaker_name": "凌风",
      "listener": "char_xin_jie",
      "text": "捷弟，你好好休息吧，你伤势一定会好的。",
      "tone": "柔声",
      "chapter": 30,
      "line_start": 16,
      "line_end": 16
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ling_feng",
      "speaker_name": "凌风",
      "listener": "char_xin_jie",
      "text": "捷弟，我是你大哥，你的大哥呀，别费心思，好好养伤！",
      "tone": "激动",
      "chapter": 30,
      "line_start": 34,
      "line_end": 34
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xin_jie",
      "speaker_name": "辛捷",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "梅……龄……侯二叔……方少魌……死了……死了。",
      "tone": "悲伤",
      "chapter": 30,
      "line_start": 38,
      "line_end": 38
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ling_feng",
      "speaker_name": "凌风",
      "listener": "char_xin_jie",
      "text": "谁死了？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 30,
      "line_start": 40,
      "line_end": 40
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xin_jie",
      "speaker_name": "辛捷",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "海……海……是……这样……跳下去的。",
      "tone": "悲伤",
      "chapter": 30,
      "line_start": 42,
      "line_end": 42
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ling_feng",
      "speaker_name": "凌风",
      "listener": "char_xin_jie",
      "text": "捷弟，你别胡思乱想啦。",
      "tone": "温柔",
      "chapter": 30,
      "line_start": 44,
      "line_end": 44
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xin_jie",
      "speaker_name": "辛捷",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "是这样……这样跳下去的，我……我眼睁睁，看到波浪……波浪卷没了……",
      "tone": "悲痛",
      "chapter": 30,
      "line_start": 46,
      "line_end": 46
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ling_feng",
      "speaker_name": "凌风",
      "listener": "char_xin_jie",
      "text": "谁跳海呀？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 30,
      "line_start": 48,
      "line_end": 48
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xin_jie",
      "speaker_name": "辛捷",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "方……方少方少魌……我……我……原是很喜欢她，很喜欢呀！",
      "tone": "悲伤",
      "chapter": 30,
      "line_start": 50,
      "line_end": 50
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ling_feng",
      "speaker_name": "凌风",
      "listener": "char_xin_jie",
      "text": "方少魌是一位姑娘，她投海自杀了吗？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 30,
      "line_start": 54,
      "line_end": 54
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ling_feng",
      "speaker_name": "凌风",
      "listener": "char_xin_jie",
      "text": "那方姑娘，定然得救了。",
      "tone": "温柔",
      "chapter": 30,
      "line_start": 58,
      "line_end": 58
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ling_feng",
      "speaker_name": "凌风",
      "listener": "char_xin_jie",
      "text": "你倒说说你怎会被关中九豪伤成这般模样？若不是靠云爷爷的灵药，此刻只怕——",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 30,
      "line_start": 102,
      "line_end": 104
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xin_jie",
      "speaker_name": "辛捷",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "关中九豪真不愧挣得了很大的名头，以众凌寡自是上策啊！下次我碰上了，哼——",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 30,
      "line_start": 106,
      "line_end": 108
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ling_feng",
      "speaker_name": "凌风",
      "listener": "char_xin_jie",
      "text": "捷弟，恭喜你啊，'梅香神剑'这外号敢情好。",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 30,
      "line_start": 112,
      "line_end": 112
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xin_jie",
      "speaker_name": "辛捷",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "可惜梅香剑已被盗去啦，只待我明日略为恢复，就立刻上崆峒去大闹一场——大哥，你也要去，也好清一清旧账。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 30,
      "line_start": 114,
      "line_end": 116
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ling_feng",
      "speaker_name": "凌风",
      "listener": "char_xin_jie",
      "text": "云爷爷的灵药端的妙绝，捷弟你受了那么重的伤，流那么多的血，竟然两天之内就完全恢复，不过捷弟，你还是休息一下较为稳当。",
      "tone": "欣慰",
      "chapter": 30,
      "line_start": 120,
      "line_end": 122
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xin_jie",
      "speaker_name": "辛捷",
      "listener": "char_ling_feng",
      "text": "大哥，咱们先暂时不到崆峒去——",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 30,
      "line_start": 126,
      "line_end": 126
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ling_feng",
      "speaker_name": "凌风",
      "listener": "char_xin_jie",
      "text": "怎么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 30,
      "line_start": 128,
      "line_end": 128
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xin_jie",
      "speaker_name": "辛捷",
      "listener": "char_ling_feng",
      "text": "咱们不是答应那苏姑娘要去看她一次么？我想厉老贼既是崆峒一派之掌门，咱们随时去找他，他总不能缩头不见，是以怕还是先去山东看看苏姑娘——",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 30,
      "line_start": 130,
      "line_end": 130
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_dian_xiao_er",
      "speaker_name": "店小二",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "两位英雄可是接了武当赤阳道长的邀请要上奎山的？",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 30,
      "line_start": 156,
      "line_end": 158
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xin_jie",
      "speaker_name": "辛捷",
      "listener": "char_dian_xiao_er",
      "text": "你怎么知道赤阳道长？上奎山干么啊？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 30,
      "line_start": 160,
      "line_end": 162
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_dian_xiao_er",
      "speaker_name": "店小二",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "原来二位爷还不知道呀，这事端的是轰动天下哩。",
      "tone": "得意",
      "chapter": 30,
      "line_start": 164,
      "line_end": 166
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xin_jie",
      "speaker_name": "辛捷",
      "listener": "char_dian_xiao_er",
      "text": "什么事要轰动天下啊！",
      "tone": "好奇",
      "chapter": 30,
      "line_start": 168,
      "line_end": 168
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_dian_xiao_er",
      "speaker_name": "店小二",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "这几天成千的英雄好汉都路过咱们这里赶往奎山，小的是听几位英雄在这店里谈天才知道的，说是那赤阳道长发了请帖请天下英雄聚集奎山，说要合力对付两个什么西方夷族来的人物，我说这就怪啦，两个外国蛮子来了也要惊动这许多英雄好汉去……",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 30,
      "line_start": 170,
      "line_end": 170
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xin_jie",
      "speaker_name": "辛捷",
      "listener": "char_dian_xiao_er",
      "text": "是什么样的蛮子啊？",
      "tone": "好奇",
      "chapter": 30,
      "line_start": 172,
      "line_end": 172
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_dian_xiao_er",
      "speaker_name": "店小二",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "小的还是听这位爷说的呢，你们问这位爷他准知道得清楚。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 30,
      "line_start": 176,
      "line_end": 178
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wu_lin_ren_wu",
      "speaker_name": "武林人物",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "阁下有何事询问在下？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 30,
      "line_start": 182,
      "line_end": 182
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ling_feng",
      "speaker_name": "吴凌风",
      "listener": "char_wu_ling_ming",
      "text": "咱们在说那两个外国蛮夷的不识好歹——",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 30,
      "line_start": 186,
      "line_end": 186
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wu_lin_ren_wu",
      "speaker_name": "武林人物",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "是啊，咱们这次要是赌斗输了，那么中原武林人物可就永远翻不得身啦——",
      "tone": "担心",
      "chapter": 30,
      "line_start": 192,
      "line_end": 192
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wu_lin_ren_wu",
      "speaker_name": "武林人物",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "试想这两个蛮子要咱们中原武林公认他们的什么'金伯胜佛'为武林盟主，还要十五位武林鼎鼎大名的人物跟他们回去朝拜那'金伯胜佛'，这等气咱们怎么受得住？不过这次见赤阳道长那郑重的情形，只怕这两个蛮子功夫高得很哩——",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 30,
      "line_start": 196,
      "line_end": 198
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wu_lin_ren_wu",
      "speaker_name": "武林人物",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "这两个蛮子想必是出身野蛮之邦，否则怎会如此欺人太甚？",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 30,
      "line_start": 202,
      "line_end": 202
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wu_lin_ren_wu",
      "speaker_name": "武林人物",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "这两个蛮子是从天竺来的，他们还说：'听说近几十年中原最了得的一个是河洛一剑吴诏云，一个是七妙神君梅山民，可惜这两人死了，否则也好叫他们见识见识天竺的武艺。'唉，真可惜这两位奇人死了，否则倒好叫这蛮子见识见识中原的武艺哩！",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 30,
      "line_start": 206,
      "line_end": 210
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xin_jie",
      "speaker_name": "辛捷",
      "listener": "char_ling_feng",
      "text": "这个天竺来的蛮子好横，咱们索性到奎山去让他见识见识河洛一剑和七妙神君的功夫。",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 30,
      "line_start": 214,
      "line_end": 216
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ling_feng",
      "speaker_name": "吴凌风",
      "listener": "char_xin_jie",
      "text": "咱这几日赶路打山路小径里走，出了这么一桩大事竟不知道。",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 30,
      "line_start": 218,
      "line_end": 220
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xin_jie",
      "speaker_name": "辛捷",
      "listener": "char_ling_feng",
      "text": "大哥，方才上山时你可听见一条人影在山下疾奔而来？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 30,
      "line_start": 238,
      "line_end": 240
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ling_feng",
      "speaker_name": "凌风",
      "listener": "char_xin_jie",
      "text": "是啊，我瞧那人轻功俊极，只是方才不便说话，所以没出声。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 30,
      "line_start": 242,
      "line_end": 244
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xin_jie",
      "speaker_name": "辛捷",
      "listener": "char_ling_feng",
      "text": "我瞧那人影九成是那'武林之秀'——",
      "tone": "低语",
      "chapter": 30,
      "line_start": 246,
      "line_end": 246
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chi_yang_dao_zhang",
      "speaker_name": "赤阳道长",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "各位请一静——",
      "tone": "严肃",
      "chapter": 30,
      "line_start": 258,
      "line_end": 258
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chi_yang_dao_zhang",
      "speaker_name": "赤阳道长",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "天竺高手已经到临——",
      "tone": "严肃",
      "chapter": 30,
      "line_start": 264,
      "line_end": 264
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jia_da_er",
      "speaker_name": "加大尔",
      "listener": "char_ru_sheng_yi_ren",
      "text": "阿喜米，估什摩诃尔，乌法各各哩查。",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 30,
      "line_start": 268,
      "line_end": 270
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ru_sheng_yi_ren",
      "speaker_name": "儒生夷人",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "不料中原还真有些人材呢——",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 30,
      "line_start": 288,
      "line_end": 288
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ru_sheng_yi_ren",
      "speaker_name": "儒生夷人",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "咱们兄弟久慕中原武学，今日中原豪侠齐聚一室，正好令咱们兄弟一开眼界，同时，咱们愿意在这里候教两场，只要咱们败了一场，我兄弟两人立刻掉头走路，要是我们二场全胜，哈哈，下面的话早已告诉武当赤阳道长了",
      "tone": "豪迈",
      "chapter": 30,
      "line_start": 296,
      "line_end": 297
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chi_yang_dao_zhang",
      "speaker_name": "赤阳道长",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "今日是咱们五大剑派生死存亡的关头了，若是我们几人败了……唉，不必说了。",
      "tone": "担心",
      "chapter": 30,
      "line_start": 302,
      "line_end": 304
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ku_an_shang_ren",
      "speaker_name": "苦庵上人",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "说不得咱们只好把几根老骨头拼上了，咱们忝为武林五大宗派门人，若是不身先士卒，只怕要令天下好汉齿冷——",
      "tone": "严肃",
      "chapter": 30,
      "line_start": 310,
      "line_end": 310
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chi_yang_dao_zhang",
      "speaker_name": "赤阳道长",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "厉兄怎么还没有来，否则凭他那手崆峒神剑当可打头一阵，挫挫他们的锐气。",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 30,
      "line_start": 316,
      "line_end": 318
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ru_sheng_yi_ren",
      "speaker_name": "儒生夷人",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "第一场由我师兄加大尔出阵，中原英雄哪位出场？",
      "tone": "豪迈",
      "chapter": 30,
      "line_start": 322,
      "line_end": 322
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ku_an_shang_ren",
      "speaker_name": "苦庵上人",
      "listener": "char_chi_yang_dao_zhang",
      "text": "还是让老衲去接这蛮子几招吧，道长和谢贤侄请为我掠阵——",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 30,
      "line_start": 330,
      "line_end": 330
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chi_yang_dao_zhang",
      "speaker_name": "赤阳道长",
      "listener": "char_ku_an_shang_ren",
      "text": "此役关系非同小可，上人千万不要存客气之心。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 30,
      "line_start": 334,
      "line_end": 336
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ku_an_shang_ren",
      "speaker_name": "苦庵上人",
      "listener": "char_jia_da_er",
      "text": "贫僧峨嵋苦庵，愿接这位加施主的高招。",
      "tone": "严肃",
      "chapter": 30,
      "line_start": 340,
      "line_end": 342
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jia_da_er",
      "speaker_name": "加大尔",
      "listener": "char_ru_sheng_yi_ren",
      "text": "各希米尔，雅华巴拉可耶？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 30,
      "line_start": 348,
      "line_end": 348
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ru_sheng_yi_ren",
      "speaker_name": "儒生夷人",
      "listener": "char_jia_da_er",
      "text": "弗希哩，希阿罗峨嵋更色。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 30,
      "line_start": 352,
      "line_end": 352
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ling_feng",
      "speaker_name": "吴凌风",
      "listener": "char_xin_jie",
      "text": "这蛮子武功大是古怪，只怕苦庵上人接不下百招。",
      "tone": "低语",
      "chapter": 30,
      "line_start": 378,
      "line_end": 380
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ku_an_shang_ren",
      "speaker_name": "苦庵上人",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "这一场贫僧认输——",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 30,
      "line_start": 422,
      "line_end": 422
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "众人",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "武林之秀！",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 30,
      "line_start": 436,
      "line_end": 436
    }
  ],
